subSubSection.paragraph:
Genitalia. Sternite 7 medially with wide, V-shaped notch; lateral process elongate, acuminate ( Figs 8a, b&d , Wapadsberg, wide lateral apices; Fig. 8c , Loodsberg, narrow lateral apices), rarely bipinnate. Valvula 1 lanceolate ( Fig. 8e ), imbricate sculpture ( Fig. 8f ). Valvula 2 with fine serration (
Fig. 8g &h
), valvifer 2 as in Fig. 8i . Valvula 3 with fine setae ( Fig. 8j&k ).

